import React, { use} from 'react' import PropTypes from 'prop-types' const ProductView = props => { const product = props.product const [previewImg, setPreviewImg] = useState(product.image01) return (
setPreviewImg (product.image01)} >
setPreviewImg (product.image02)} >
) } ProductView.propTypes = { product: PropTypes.object.isRequired } export default ProductView
